{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place butter into mixing bowl and melt <b>2 min\/70°C\/speed 2<b>.","Add milk, water, plain flour, eggs and salt and mix <b>10 sec\/speed 4<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula then mix a further <b>10 sec\/speed 4<b>. The batter should have the consistency of liquid cream. If it seems too thick, add a little milk. Allow batter to rest in refrigerator for at least 30 minutes before using.","Lightly grease a non-stick frying pan with butter and heat on medium-high. Pour in a small ladle of batter, twirling the pan as you pour to cover the base of the pan completely. Cook for 2 - 3 minutes or until edges of crêpe are light golden. Turn crêpe over and cook for a further 1 minute. Transfer to a ThermoServer or a plate and cover with a kitchen towel to keep warm. Repeat with remaining batter. Serve warm."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["50 g butter, plus extra for frying","500 g milk","200 g water","250 g plain flour","4 eggs","1 pinch salt"]}],"id":"r66931","imageLink":"https:\/\/2.bp.blogspot.com\/-wWA3ruNtfgU\/XZXYsps3_sI\/AAAAAAAAgA4\/FEToPKsTVRkQyA8i-ZXNzMcB5WNixgJiwCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_S5BBoH_Ph6mYC1ry.png","title":"Crêpes","publishedAt":"2014-09-05T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"7 g","fat":"11 g","uom":"per 1 piece","carbohydrates":"21 g","calories":"872 kJ \/ 209 kcal"},"usefulItems":"turner \/ fish slice, ThermoServer, non-stick frying pan (22 cm), kitchen towel, ladle, refrigerator, stove","hintsAndTricks":["To substitute butter with oil, omit step 1 and add 50 g oil along with all other ingredients in step 2. Use oil to grease the frying pan in step 3 and proceed as per recipe.","<strong><\/strong>Crêpes can be served with sweet or savoury fillings.","Crêpes can be frozen for later use. Place a piece of baking paper or plastic wrap between each crêpe before freezing so they can be easily defrosted. After defrosting, wrap crêpes in aluminium foil and warm in a preheated oven (150ºC) for 5-10 minutes.","<strong>Vanilla crêpes:<\/strong> add 40 g vanilla sugar in step 2 and proceed as per recipe.","<strong>Orange crêpes:<\/strong> add 1 tsp grated orange zest in step 2 and proceed as per recipe.","<strong>Rum-flavoured crêpes:<\/strong> add 80 g sugar and 2 tbsp rum in step 2 and proceed as per recipe.","<strong>Gluten free crêpes:<\/strong> substitute flour with buckwheat flour and proceed as per recipe.","<strong>Dairy free crêpes:<\/strong> substitute butter with 40 g oil and milk with soy milk. Place all ingredients into mixing bowl and combine <strong>20 sec\/speed 4<\/strong>, then proceed as per recipe."],"basicInfo":["easy","45m","1h 15m","10 pieces"]}